title: Star Wars: Ewoks complete series 1985-1986
description: This is the 1985 Star Wars: Ewoks animated series. It ran for two seasons but only the first season seems to be available on TPB. Since the series has only ever had a botched and incomplete DVD release I think it is important to, for the first time, have the entire series available together. This is the entire first season taken from the already posted torrent plus I ripped the second season in a remastered form off of YouTube and compiled them together. Enjoy
